                     <interp inst="t18480103-493-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>, stealing 2 dead fowls, value 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18480103-name-528" type="victimName">
