                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I produce a certificate of Riley's former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted Oct.</hi>, 1847, <hi rend="italic">and confined one month and whipped</hi>)—I was present at the trial—he is the person.</p>
